# NeonAI Amazon Language Plugin
Language Plugin for Amazon language detection and translation

# Configuration:

```yaml
keys:
  amazon: {"key_id": "<AWS_KEY_ID>",
           "secret_key": "<AWS_SECRET_KEY>",
           "region": "us-west-2"}
```

